{"tid":1784801,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭月娥今日將向習近平、李克強匯報香港最新情況","createTime":"2019-12-16T02:50:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T13:50:37.000Z","uid":212626,"like":2,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"01c754c71456f8b3e17b3590b8d565431a00249b","tid":1784801,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T02:50:39.000Z","msg":"正在北京述職的行政長官林鄭月娥，早上將到人民大會堂向總理李克強匯報香港的最新情況。<br />\n<br />\n她早上離開酒店時沒有回應傳媒提問，包括前日晚上是否與國務院副總理韓正見面，及會否向總理李克強匯報昨晚再發生警民衝突等。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥下午亦會與國家主席習近平會面，明日返港。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1497883-20191216.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1497883-20191216.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=tTL%2BVp%2FfZAnEQ6lEIPL8hgWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=5d211f5e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1497883-20191216.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=d6f43226\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1497883-20191216.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"6b12a83e086780f542855f618ebff089d38fed82","tid":1784801,"uid":11454,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T02:52:43.000Z","msg":"準備又欺上瞞下<br />\n通常匯報完就淋火水<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc49093b1b72646ac30293b44e5dfc78e36b53d4","tid":1784801,"uid":19552,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T02:53:38.000Z","msg":"做台戲話香港市民上下一心愛國愛黨愛警<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcd78bcf85e62a571896964695bea538ddea6e00","tid":1784801,"uid":7818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6b12a83e086780f542855f618ebff089d38fed82","tid":1784801,"uid":11454,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T02:52:43.000Z","msg":"準備又欺上瞞下<br />\n通常匯報完就淋火水<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"repl